CatDescriptText: This group of women, except for the woman to Gloria's right, were known as the D.I.'s; Delightfully Insane. Many people tried to guess the meaning of this group, but no one ever did.
TitMainTitle: Six women gathered on sofas and chairs inside Gloria Golden Grate's home, including from left to right, Margaret West Watson, Evelyn Christian, unknown, Gloria Golden Grate, Anna Simmons "Birdie" Dunlap, Junita Drakein interior with two toned curtains
